These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
Flower: begonia, balloon-flower, amaryllis, rose
Pet: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
Movie-Genre: fantasy, superhero, romance, drama
1. Movie-Genre:romance is on the left of Pet:ferret##1
2. Movie-Genre:drama == Pet:cat##1
3. Flower:amaryllis is on the far left##1
4. Flower:begonia is on the far right##1
5. Pet:ferret is between Movie-Genre:romance and Flower:balloon-flower##2
6. Movie-Genre:superhero == Pet:lizard##1
7. Pet:cat is on the right of Pet:ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | amaryllis | rose  | balloon-flower | begonia  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | fantasy | drama       | superhero |

